Federation (IAAF) announced on Sunday that the world indoor
athletics championship in 2005 were rescheuled to 2004.
</P>
<P>
The 2001 version of the competition will be hosted by Lisbon,
Portugal.
</P>
<P>
A two-day IAAF meeting will decide the hosts of the 2003
championships among Birmingham, England and Budapest, Hungary.
</P>
