industry this year should be 12 percent, to attain an income of
450 billion yuan.
</P>
<P>
The country is expected to accommodate 29 million overseas
tourists this year and earn 15 billion US dollars in foreign
exchange. This means that the number of domestic tourists should
reach 740 million, and the income from tourism should be 330
billion yuan (about 40 billion US dollars). 
