<TEXT>
<P>
BEIRUT, April 2 (Xinhua) -- Syrian Foreign Minister Faruk Shareh
arrived here Sunday morning to deliver a message from Syrian
President Hafez al-Assad to Lebanese leaders, the People's Voice
radio reported.
