<HEADLINE> Congo JMC to Hold Talks in Uganda </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, April 2 (Xinhua) -- The Joint Military Commission (JMC)
on the Democratic Republic of the Congo (DRC) has announced that
it will soon hold its sixth plenary session in Kampala, Uganda,
Sunday Times of Zambia reported.
</P>
