opposing forces in the Afghan conflict and they differ in their
perceptions on the Afghan issue.
</P>
<P>
During the course of Afghan conflict Islamabad has supported
the ruing Taliban militia, while Tehran backs the anti-Taliban
Northern Alliance.
</P>
<P>
However, both Pakistan and Iran have expressed their
willingness to coordinate their positions on Afghanistan and
cooperate with each other in seeking a final settlement of the
Afghan civil war.
