President Hosni Mubarak will try to bridge the gap between the two
countries, said Syrian diplomatic sources here on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Mubarak will visit Syria and hold a summit meeting with Syrian
President Hafez al-Assad soon after he meets Israeli Prime Minister
Ehud Barak, the sources said.
</P>
<P>
